org.codice.ddf.admin.application.service

Interface ApplicationNode

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ApplicationNodeImpl

    public interface ApplicationNode
    Node for applications that is used to create a hierarchy tree that shows application dependencies.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

      Application getApplication()
      Returns the application this node is referencing.
      Set<ApplicationNode> getChildren()
      Returns the children of this application.
      ApplicationNode getParent()
      Returns the parent of the application.
      ApplicationStatus getStatus()
